<item>
 <title>Tips and Tools for Creating Infographics for Your Small Business</title>
 <link>https://info.info/newsroom/blog/tips-and-tools-creating-infographics-your-small-business</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-title field-type-ds field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;dc:title&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Tips and Tools for Creating Infographics for Your Small Business&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Infographics are a visual format that&#039;s increasingly popular. They&#039;re an effective way to share information and boost online traffic and engagement. Infographics are a great format for illustrating:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Trends and compelling industry data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;How-to instructions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Complex information that can be broken down into more digestible parts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Here are some tips and tools to help you get started with creating infographics for your small business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt; &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;Best Practices for Infographics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Choose the right medium&lt;/strong&gt;. Create an infographic when something is easier to understand illustrated than in a thousand words. For example, a map is much more effective than a textual description for sharing information related to specific locations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stick to one topic&lt;/strong&gt;. Make just a few points to make it easier to review and remember the content.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Make it easy on the eyes&lt;/strong&gt;. Use a highly readable type, simple color palettes, and a simple design.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tell a story&lt;/strong&gt;. The infographic should have a beginning (headline/intro), middle (key points), and end (conclusion/call to action).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Use stellar images&lt;/strong&gt;. The visuals and graphics must pack a punch and have an emotional impact.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt; &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;media-image&quot; height=&quot;320&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://info.info/sites/afilias-tld/files/styles/large/public/dose-media-gxGtqG5ul2g-unsplash_0.jpg?itok=FbEIoxB_&quot; /&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt; &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6 Things to Avoid&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Forcing content to fit the format. &lt;/strong&gt;If you find you need long paragraphs to make it work, an infographic might not be the ideal solution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Combining unrelated elements.&lt;/strong&gt; Make sure to group related information and data so the information doesn&#039;t become confusing and muddled.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Failing to establish a hierarchy in the design&lt;/strong&gt;. Guide readers through the infographic from top to bottom.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Not creating a compelling narrative.&lt;/strong&gt; Throwing a mix of graphics together does not an infographic make. If your readers don&#039;t discern a clear thread, they will stop reading.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Using low-resolution images and small fonts.&lt;/strong&gt; Images should be crisp and letters large enough that anyone can easily review the content.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Not catching mistakes and errors.&lt;/strong&gt; Make sure to edit and check for factual and spelling errors and design mistakes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt; &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Free Tools for Creating Infographics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;If you have some graphic design chops, great! But there are plenty of online tools that make creating an infographic a snap.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://spark.adobe.com/make/infographic-maker/&quot;&gt;Adobe Spark&lt;/a&gt; guides you through creating simple infographics to share on websites or social media. No design skills needed thanks to clean templates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.visme.co/make-infographics/&quot;&gt;Visme&lt;/a&gt; is designed for more complex infographics. Start from a template or with premade blocks that you can add custom content to.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://piktochart.com/formats/infographics/&quot;&gt;Piktochart&lt;/a&gt; uses maps and charts to tell a story. The interface is packed with icons to help turn a text story into something more visual.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.canva.com&quot;&gt;Canva&lt;/a&gt; is one of the most well-known infographics tools and comes with a variety of graphic elements, including photos, icons, and illustrations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://developers.google.com/chart/&quot;&gt;Google Charts&lt;/a&gt; enables creating data charts that you can use on your website.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt; &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;See If Infographics Work for Your Small Business&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Infographics are an effective way to share engaging information that&#039;s visually interesting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;If you haven&#039;t tried this format yet, it can be a great way to promote your small business, product, or service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-topics field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Topics:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/topics/entrepreneurship&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Entrepreneurship&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/topics/marketing&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Marketing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/topics/small-business-marketing&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Small Business Marketing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/topics/web-design&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Web Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-author-term field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Author:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/author/carrie-cousins&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot;&gt;Carrie Cousins&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
